      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. When you mention \"modern\" vs \"primitive,\" are there certain types of cultures or regions that typically fall into these categories? Like, are there specific characteristics that make a society move from the \"primitive\" stage into a \"civilized\" one?",
